<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .highlight { background: #FEF3C7; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 6px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Trial is Ending Soon</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.email }},</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Your {{ subscription.plan.name }} trial ends in {{ days_remaining }} day{{ days_remaining > 1 ? 's' : '' }}.</strong>
            </div>
            
            <p>We hope you've enjoyed using our service! Your trial will end on <strong>{{ subscription.trialEndsAt|date('M d, Y') }}</strong>.</p>
            
            <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Add a payment method to continue using {{ subscription.plan.name }}</li>
                <li>Your subscription will automatically convert to a paid plan</li>
                <li>No interruption in service</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Plan Details:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>{{ subscription.plan.name }} - {{ subscription.plan.formattedPrice }}</li>
                <li>{{ subscription.plan.teamMemberLimit ?? 'Unlimited' }} team members</li>
                <li>All {{ subscription.plan.name }} features included</li>
            </ul>
            
            <a href="{{ url('payment_methods') }}" class="button">Add Payment Method</a>
            
            <p>If you don't want to continue, no action is needed. Your trial will simply expire.</p>
            
            <p>Questions? We're here to help!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} SaaS Starter Pack. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
